{"tid":2055090,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[借account]垃圾老連扮政治中立 縱容藍絲高層撐警！","createTime":"2020-06-07T16:22:37.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-07T13:49:15.000Z","uid":46050,"like":51,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":27,"replies":[{"pid":"5ad791cb5d7c6676c7dd8c637fec68099ea09db1","tid":2055090,"uid":46050,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-07T16:22:37.000Z","msg":"是咁的，連卡佛腦細係藍就全世界都知架啦，之前都有post 話運動最勁個時老連係最遲收鋪，又安排得差攪到員工食哂TG <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n個排公司啲高層已經屌班手足話攪到無哂生意，要做多左啲垃圾安排比員工收工<br />\n<br />\n間垃圾公司內部講明唔俾公開講政治野，但有朋友圈呢排瘋轉緊既相，呢條臭閪叫jobie li, vm head,已經比fd block 哂unfriend哂，識佢既人仲話佢係公司同鋪頭大粒成日開口埋口都鬧死黃屍<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />仲係貨場 毫無避忌話抵死最好炒哂啲黃絲。之前三罷，就算無客但返得工就會有野做，班staffs 做緊野佢就屌無人幫到手，話黃絲無腦，無批判能力比人慫恿罷工，仲讚班狗做野好辛苦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />係平時開左鋪多次大大聲係鋪頭講粗口鬧人，俾人投訴過又冇事，有次講電話勁大聲「屌！」成個貨場聽到都呆哂(冇跨張 真係成層)，啲客都O撚哂，同事要立即返同客say sorry 先圓到場<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />。<br />\n<br />\n行老連攪到衰過行永安<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />賣牌子野但上網買啲discount 仲平過佢減價，大家識做啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/tsdJTM7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FtsdJTM7.jpg&h=aeda16d6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nJobie Li <br />\n老連vm head"},{"pid":"bde1091ea3ac10023067e28af217b8b5652b1b35","tid":2055090,"uid":80851,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-07T16:24:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"89faef3898c2a5a84c88536b661b63d7fd6d2d4a","tid":2055090,"uid":71341,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-07T17:14:11